'''全体进步大会党'''（{{lang-en|All Progressives Congress}}，简称APC）是[[尼日利亚|尼日利亚]]的一个政党，成立于2013年2月6日，主要是为准备[[2015年尼日利亚大选|2015年尼日利亚大选]]由多个反对党联手组建。<ref name="This Time">{{cite news|title=The Merger This Time!|url=http://pmnewsnigeria.com/2013/02/13/the-merger-this-time/|accessdate=15 February 2013|newspaper=PM News|date=13 February 2013|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028002625/https://www.pmnewsnigeria.com/2013/02/13/the-merger-this-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Agree to Merge">{{cite news|last=Maram|first=Mazen|title=Nigerian Biggest Opposition Parties Agree to Merge|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-07/nigerian-biggest-opposition-parties-merging-against-ruling-party.html|accessdate=11 February 2013|newspaper=Bloomberg|date=7 February 2013|archive-date=2014-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225012035/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-07/nigerian-biggest-opposition-parties-merging-against-ruling-party.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Welcome>{{cite news|last=Opoola|first=Murtala|title=Nigeria: Welcome, All Progressives Congress|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201302100244.html|accessdate=11 February 2013|newspaper=AllAfrica|date=10 February 2013|archive-date=2014-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225011720/http://allafrica.com/stories/201302100244.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该党总统候选人[[穆罕默杜·布哈里|穆罕默杜·布哈里]]以260万净胜票的优势赢得选举。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.inecnigeria.org/?page_id=31/|title=Election Result-Independent National Electoral Commission|date=2 April 2015|website=|publisher=INEC|access-date=7 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414082516/http://www.inecnigeria.org/?page_id=31%2F|archive-date=2015-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>3月31日，时任总统[[古德勒克·乔纳森|古德勒克·乔纳森]]承认败选。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32139858 |title=Nigeria election: Muhammadu Buhari wins |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date=31 March 2015 |website= |publisher=BBC News |access-date=31 March 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331214138/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32139858 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这是尼日利亚政治历史上首次出现反对派政党成功在大选中打败执政党，国家权力交接以和平方式完成的情况。<ref name="Nigeria makes history in presidential election">{{cite news|title=Nigeria makes history in presidential election|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/nigeria-makes-history-in-presidential-election/|accessdate=31 March 2015|date=31 March 2015|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022200230/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/nigeria-makes-history-in-presidential-election/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，全体进步大会党还获得了[[尼日利亚参议院|参议院]]和[[尼日利亚众议院|众议院]]的多数席位，但是并没有拿到足以推翻[[尼日利亚人民民主党|人民民主党]]杯葛议案能力的绝对多数。<ref name="APC wins 214 House of Reps' seats">{{cite news|title=APC wins 214 House of Reps' seats|url=http://www.punchng.com/news/apc-wins-214-house-of-reps-seats/|accessdate=8 April 2015|newspaper=Punch|date=8 April 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421212204/http://www.punchng.com/news/apc-wins-214-house-of-reps-seats/|archivedate=2015年4月21日}}</ref><ref name="APC wins 64 seats in Senate">{{cite news|title=APC wins 64 seats in Senate|url=http://www.punchng.com/news/apc-wins-64-seats-in-senate/|accessdate=1 April 2015|newspaper=Punch|date=1 April 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401184739/http://www.punchng.com/news/apc-wins-64-seats-in-senate/|archivedate=2015年4月1日}}</ref>

== 组成 ==
该党成立于2013年2月，是尼日利亚三大反对党——[[尼日利亚行动大会党|尼日利亚行动大会党]]（ACN）、[[进步变革大会党|进步变革大会党]]（CPC）、[[全尼日利亚人民党|全尼日利亚人民党]]（ANPP）连同[[全面进步大联盟|全面进步大联盟]]（APGA）一部分成员结盟的结果，以此对抗执政党[[尼日利亚人民民主党|人民民主党]]。<ref name="Risks in merger">{{cite news|last=Agomuo|first=Zebulon|title=Possible risks in opposition merger ahead 2015|url=http://www.businessdayonline.com/NG/index.php/business-intelligence/51332-possible-risks-in-opposition-merger-ahead-2015|accessdate=11 February 2013|newspaper=Business Daily|date=11 February 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130214053440/http://www.businessdayonline.com/NG/index.php/business-intelligence/51332-possible-risks-in-opposition-merger-ahead-2015|archivedate=2013年2月14日}}</ref><ref name="Approves Merger">{{cite news|last=Akor|first=Ambrose|title=Nigeria's Key Opposition Party Approves Merger Plan|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-18/nigeria-s-key-opposition-party-approves-merger-plan.html|accessdate=6 May 2013|newspaper=Bloomberg|date=18 April 2013|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407071111/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-18/nigeria-s-key-opposition-party-approves-merger-plan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>合并决议由行动大会党代表{{link-en|汤姆·伊基米|Tom Ikimi}}，全面进步大联盟代表、参议员{{link-en|安尼·奥库科旺|Annie Okonkwo}}，全尼日利亚人民党合并委员会主席、前[[卡诺州|卡诺州]]州长、伊斯兰教学者{{link-en|伊布拉辛·谢卡劳|Ibrahim Shekarau}}以及进步变革大会党合并委员会主席贾巴·谢胡共同签署。<ref name="New Party">{{cite news|last=Agbakwuru|first=Johnbosco|title=Nigeria: New Party – Buhari, Tinubu, Threaten Jonathan With Armoured Personnel Carrier, APC|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201302100028.html|accessdate=12 February 2013|newspaper=AllAfrica|date=10 February 2013|archive-date=2014-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214090149/http://allafrica.com/stories/201302100028.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，在该党2015年历史性大选胜利之前不到两年的时间里，安尼·奥库科旺、汤姆·伊基米和伊布拉辛·谢卡劳纷纷退出该党，转投人民民主党。<ref name="“APC lacks internal democracy”– Ex-Deputy Chairman, Annie Okonkwo rejoins PDP">{{cite news|title="APC lacks internal democracy" – Ex-Deputy Chairman, Annie Okonkwo rejoins PDP|url=http://dailypost.ng/2014/10/25/apc-lacks-internal-democracy-ex-deputy-chairman-annie-okonkwo-rejoins-pdp/|accessdate=8 April 2015|newspaper=Daily post|date=24 October 2014|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917221019/https://dailypost.ng/2014/10/25/apc-lacks-internal-democracy-ex-deputy-chairman-annie-okonkwo-rejoins-pdp/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tom Ikimi dumps APC, attacks Tinubu">{{cite news|title=Tom Ikimi dumps APC, attacks Tinubu|url=http://www.premiumtimesng.com/opinion/167340-tom-ikimi-dumps-apc-attacks-tinubu.html/|accessdate=8 April 2015|newspaper=Premium Times|date=27 August 2014|archive-date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327055105/http://www.premiumtimesng.com/opinion/167340-tom-ikimi-dumps-apc-attacks-tinubu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BREAKING: Ex-Kano Governor, Shekarau, dumps APC for PDP">{{cite news|title=BREAKING: Ex-Kano Governor, Shekarau, dumps APC for PDP|url=http://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/154192-breaking-ex-kano-governor-shekarau-dumps-apc-pdp.html/|accessdate=8 April 2015|newspaper=Premium Times|date=29 January 2014|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309055942/http://www.premiumtimesng.com/news/154192-breaking-ex-kano-governor-shekarau-dumps-apc-pdp.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年7月31日，全体进步大会党的组党申请得到大选主管机构{{link-en|独立国家选举委员会|Independent National Electoral Commission}}（INEC）的批准，该党撤回了原来三个党派（尼日利亚行动大会党、进步变革大会党、全尼日利亚人民党）的运营许可。2013年3月曾有报道称另外两个组织——非洲人民大会党（African Peoples Congress）和全体爱国公民党（All Patriotic Citizens）——均向独立国家选举委员会递交过注册申请，且简写均为“APC”，这被认为是意图在2015年大选前阻挠反对党的联合。<ref name="Congress meet over APC">{{cite news|last=Owete|first=Festus|title=INEC, All Progressives Congress meet over APC|url=http://premiumtimesng.com/news/126185-inec-all-progressives-congress-meet-over-apc.html|accessdate=25 March 2013|newspaper=[[Premium_Times|Premium Times]]|date=21 March 2013|archive-date=2013-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325120739/http://premiumtimesng.com/news/126185-inec-all-progressives-congress-meet-over-apc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年4月，曾有报道称该党曾考虑更名为尼日利亚全体进步大会党（APCN），以避免节外生枝。<ref name="APCN as new name">{{cite news|title=All Progressives Congress may adopt APCN as new name|url=http://www.osundefender.org/?p=96711|accessdate=2 April 2013|newspaper=Osun Defender|date=1 April 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404000036/http://www.osundefender.org/?p=96711|archivedate=2013年4月4日}}</ref>

2013年11月，五名时任[[尼日利亚州长列表|州长]]脱离人民民主党，转投全体进步大会党，此外，由于同其他较小的反对党的合并，又有49名议员加入该党阵营。<ref name="In Political Earthquake, 5 PDP Govs Defect to APC">{{cite news|title=In Political Earthquake, 5 PDP Govs Defect to APC|url=http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/in-political-earthquake-5-pdp-govs-defect-to-apc/165332/|accessdate=8 April 2015|newspaper=This Day Live|date=27 November 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408080529/http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/in-political-earthquake-5-pdp-govs-defect-to-apc/165332|archivedate=2015年4月8日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/49-house-members-decamp-to-apc/165278/|title=49 House   Members   Decamp to APC, Articles - THISDAY LIVE|publisher=|accessdate=1 April 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218033435/http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/49-house-members-decamp-to-apc/165278/|archivedate=2015年2月18日}}</ref><ref>[http://www.punchng.com/news/pdps-loss-apcs-gain/ John Alechenu, "PDP’s loss, APC’s gain"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.punchng.com/news/pdps-loss-apcs-gain/ |date=20131127124614 }}, ''Punch'', 27 November 2013.</ref>这本来会使全体进步大会党在[[尼日利亚众议院|尼日利亚众议院]]拥有186个席位，在360个总席位中占微弱多数；但是之后的政治争论，以及来自议会之外政治派别及相关利益人的压力，使得该党最终只增添了37个席位，这使得全体进步大会党拥有172个席位，相比于人民民主党的171席仅有微弱多数优势（但是一些同人民民主党结盟的小党派占有剩余席位）。<ref>[http://www.punchng.com/news/lawmakers-jubiliate-as-37-pdp-reps-defect-to-apc/ John Ameh, "Lawmakers jubiliate as 37 PDP Reps defect to APC"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.punchng.com/news/lawmakers-jubiliate-as-37-pdp-reps-defect-to-apc/ |date=20131218134435 }}, ''Punch'', 18 December 2013.</ref>在2015年1月15日，众议院在长期休会后重启议事，该党共有179名成员出席，这进一步确立了其多数席位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.olufamous.com/2015/01/apc-finally-defeats-pdp-in-house-of.html|title=APC finally defeats PDP in House of Reps, Takes the Majority - OluFamous.Com|author=Olu Famous|work=Olu Famous|accessdate=1 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214947/http://www.olufamous.com/2015/01/apc-finally-defeats-pdp-in-house-of.html|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

